WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.667 --> 00:00:02.093
Evening family.

00:00:02.093 --> 00:00:04.320
Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:04.760 --> 00:00:06.520
We're going to pray.

00:00:06.787 --> 00:00:11.840
We have work to do, as everybody can see on the news.

00:00:11.840 --> 00:00:22.987
As I've been praying over all this today—I made those two videos for you yesterday—I had a dream last night.

00:00:22.987 --> 00:00:24.343
The Lord visited me.

00:00:24.674 --> 00:00:36.930
It was actually an encounter I've never had before, but it shook me a little bit because it was instruction and correction from one of my prayer generals.

00:00:37.185 --> 00:00:50.580
It was amazing, and I'm not going to get into it until I understand it all, but I was visited by somebody and the Lord spoke to me in a dream through this individual; it was correction regarding some things.

00:00:51.100 --> 00:01:07.845
I know that probably won't make sense to some of you because this is like spiritual algebra, but I'm going to go a different direction tonight with some of the things the Lord has instructed me to do.

00:01:19.590 --> 00:01:19.740
I thought this was Carmex for your lips.

00:01:26.991 --> 00:01:27.253
I sat here and thought, 'What kind of new lip balm is this?

00:01:27.253 --> 00:01:33.925
' So I'm putting it on my lips and my son said, 'Dad, that's glue.

00:01:33.925 --> 00:01:35.764
' I said, 'Oh, glue stick.

00:01:54.800 --> 00:01:55.384
Duh.

00:01:55.384 --> 00:02:03.510
' I had to wipe my face off real quick because it was stinging.

00:02:03.520 --> 00:02:08.759
Regarding the encounter, I don't want to talk about that.

00:02:09.759 --> 00:02:15.824
I'm just going to give you some scripture that I've been meditating on: Psalm 29:11.

00:02:15.824 --> 00:02:30.720
'The Lord will give strength unto his people; the Lord will bless his people with peace.

00:02:30.720 --> 00:02:35.620
' Right now, I believe that scripture stands really strong for me.

00:02:35.620 --> 00:02:41.114
The Lord will give his people peace and strength.

00:02:43.385 --> 00:02:47.400
Right now, we need strength and peace.

00:02:47.400 --> 00:02:51.010
But I know what the Lord is instructing me because I asked, 'What do you want me to say tonight?

00:02:51.010 --> 00:02:58.240
' He said, 'Remind them: don't pray the news.

00:02:58.240 --> 00:03:01.519
' If you're praying the news, you're behind.

00:03:01.519 --> 00:03:09.030
Everything that we have seen over the last year and a half led up to this point.

00:03:10.200 --> 00:03:28.239
We've been praying over this for weeks—what the Holy Spirit warned us about concerning drones, missile attacks, and Tel Aviv—and yesterday, what the Lord showed us about Taiwan.

00:03:29.680 --> 00:03:32.519
We're praying into the future.

00:03:32.519 --> 00:03:42.560
We don't pray into the past and the present; we're praying into the future and what God has for us weeks from now.

00:03:42.560 --> 00:03:45.650
So, we're not going to camp around what the news is telling us.

00:03:45.650 --> 00:03:52.640
Regarding Ayatollah Khamenei, I rejoice that a dictator, an evil man, is no longer in power.

00:03:52.640 --> 00:03:56.840
I pray he found Jesus in the last seconds of his life.

00:03:56.840 --> 00:03:59.400
If he didn't, he's in hell.

00:03:59.796 --> 00:04:09.440
We know that God had His hand in this to remove evil men from torturing Christians and the underground church.

00:04:10.400 --> 00:04:28.280
Great persecution was coming on the church of Iran over the last few decades, and we know what the Lord showed us prior to this: the Lord said, 'I want to bring a great revival to the people of Iran.

00:04:28.280 --> 00:04:31.035
' In doing so, there will be a regime change.

00:04:31.035 --> 00:04:41.040
There's going to be a shaking in Iran, Pakistan, Afghanistan, and all of the Arab nations.

00:04:45.040 --> 00:04:47.200
Here we are, seeing this.

00:04:47.200 --> 00:04:47.560
Why?

00:04:47.560 --> 00:04:52.835
Because the Lord said, 'Brandon, you're not waiting on me to come back; I'm waiting on you.

00:04:52.835 --> 00:04:55.600
Bring in my harvest and I'll come and get you.

00:04:55.600 --> 00:04:57.759
' The harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few.

00:04:57.759 --> 00:05:04.280
What we're about to see is the superhighway above us with translations.

00:05:04.280 --> 00:05:17.853
If you are walking with the Father, you're going to be here and you're going to be there, and we're going to be ministering to people because He said there's been a door that's been closed to the body of Christ for so long.

00:05:18.119 --> 00:05:24.360
In the days ahead, I'm going to open this door and it's going to flood wide the gates.

00:05:24.585 --> 00:05:36.720
You're going to see one of the greatest harvests of souls throughout South America—Cuba, Colombia, and Costa Rica—all of it.

00:05:38.440 --> 00:05:43.600
I saw a major harvest of souls through Brazil.

00:05:47.640 --> 00:05:52.010
I'm telling you, ladies and gentlemen, after this is over, Cuba is next.

00:05:52.385 --> 00:05:55.560
It could happen at the same time.

00:05:55.805 --> 00:05:58.870
This is what we were praying into over the last 48 hours.

00:06:00.760 --> 00:06:04.200
We're praying for the leadership of Cuba to change.

00:06:04.503 --> 00:06:21.745
We're praying for Claudia to be removed, for a new leader who looks like Antonio Banderas—a great, conservative leader—to rise up in Mexico, and for the drug cartel to be dealt with.

00:06:21.745 --> 00:06:36.600
I saw three more leaders being taken out in the days ahead, and mercenary groups coming in, hired by family members to come and find their children who are being trafficked.

00:06:36.600 --> 00:06:43.680
I saw a young girl last night who was blonde-headed, and the Lord said, 'Pray for this young girl.

00:06:43.680 --> 00:06:48.405
' I saw corrupt law enforcement involved in this and all kinds of things.

00:06:48.405 --> 00:06:54.629
If you go back and watch that video, that was a very detailed vision of what we're going to be praying.

00:06:57.000 --> 00:07:00.693
It felt like, 'Lord, why are you not concerned about what's going on right now?

00:07:00.693 --> 00:07:03.680
' No, you've already prayed over that.

00:07:03.680 --> 00:07:05.280
That's old news.

00:07:05.280 --> 00:07:10.240
That's going to be at the bottom of the birdcage in the next couple of days.

00:07:11.011 --> 00:07:14.320
The bird's going to use that as toilet paper.

00:07:14.320 --> 00:07:21.880
You don't want to be praying toilet paper; you want to be praying what I'm calling you to, way ahead in advance.

00:07:22.183 --> 00:07:27.000
That's why if you're following the Spirit of God, those that are the sons of God are led by the Spirit of God.

00:07:30.858 --> 00:07:34.504
I believe that's where we are as the body of Christ.

00:07:34.504 --> 00:07:35.427
We're playing whack-a-mole.

00:07:36.947 --> 00:07:43.560
We know where the mole is coming from and we hit it with that stick right before he sticks his head out.

00:07:44.449 --> 00:07:52.080
The Lord is telling us right now to pray over this revival concerning our churches.

00:07:52.080 --> 00:07:58.100
He has Easter on our hearts to pray over the 250-year anniversary.

00:07:58.100 --> 00:08:00.340
We're praying against anti-Semitism.

00:08:00.340 --> 00:08:10.389
He's warned us about that spreading throughout the nation, Australia, and the world—great persecution against the Jewish people for what's happening today.

00:08:10.389 --> 00:08:22.360
I saw great protests and anti-Semitism making it very hard for Jewish people to live in communities around the United States and the world.

00:08:22.700 --> 00:08:29.040
As this happened, I saw them being uprooted and taken back to Israel.

00:08:29.337 --> 00:08:31.919
The Lord said, 'This is biblical.

00:08:31.919 --> 00:08:39.240
' So, we're not worried about what we see on the news right now.

00:08:39.680 --> 00:08:40.120
Why?

00:08:50.773 --> 00:08:51.067
Because the Lord will give strength unto His people and bless them with peace.

00:08:51.067 --> 00:09:00.080
We're at peace; we're not upset because we know what's coming before it comes.

00:09:10.410 --> 00:09:10.605
The true watchmen are warning you.

00:09:10.605 --> 00:09:21.080
If you're following false prophets, they don't know; they're giving you some sugarcoated word and everything's going to be okay.

00:09:21.080 --> 00:09:26.550
I'm not here to tell you everything's going to be okay.

00:09:26.550 --> 00:09:38.223
I'm telling you it's time for the church to get a backbone like a crowbar and take dominion and authority, or you're going to be in trouble.

00:09:49.331 --> 00:09:51.480
The Lord said great dark days are upon the world, but behold, it's time for the church to arise and shine, for the light has come and the glory of the Lord is risen on us, church.

00:09:51.480 --> 00:10:01.400
But it's going to take people rising up and being who they're supposed to be in these last days and saying, "Thus far, Satan, and no further.

00:10:01.400 --> 00:10:03.920
You're not going to mess with me.

00:10:03.920 --> 00:10:07.440
You're not going to mess with my children.

00:10:07.440 --> 00:10:09.920
You're not going to mess with my finances.

00:10:09.920 --> 00:10:16.320
You're going to let go of it in the name of Jesus.

00:10:16.320 --> 00:10:20.173
We have dominion and authority over you.

00:10:21.320 --> 00:10:25.290
I'm seated with him in the heavenlies far above all principalities and powers.

00:10:25.290 --> 00:10:29.860
" I talked to Sister Billy today on the phone.

00:10:29.860 --> 00:10:34.640
I sure love my spiritual mama.

00:10:34.640 --> 00:10:49.640
When you talk to the elders, I always bounce things off of them to see where they are, where the pulse is, and everything.

00:10:49.640 --> 00:10:55.510
And she said, "Brandon, did you not know?

00:10:55.510 --> 00:10:59.264
" Let me see her text.

00:11:11.827 --> 00:11:12.084
