00:11:26.400 --> 00:11:26.840
I didn't read over this very well, so please don't butcher me for reading badly.

00:11:39.867 --> 00:11:40.160
She said, "This is Shabbat.

00:11:43.280 --> 00:11:43.600
The weekly portion read in the synagogues was from Deuteronomy 25:17-19.

00:11:43.600 --> 00:12:06.130
" She was talking about where we are in these end times and how significant the Ayatollah Khamenei being removed at this exact day going into the third with the blood moon on this time frame.

00:12:06.130 --> 00:12:09.545
Folks, do you realize how close Jesus is to coming back?

00:12:09.545 --> 00:12:34.930
That's why I try to teach you, and I would love to have her on one day so she could teach you all about the Greek, the Hebrew, and all that, because she is an expert at it, and going over Haman and how he was dealt with.

00:12:38.255 --> 00:12:39.040
I look at the type and shadow, the mirror of where we are.

00:12:43.587 --> 00:12:43.782
What happened today is a mirror of what happened in the Bible.

00:12:48.260 --> 00:12:48.545
It's amazing.

00:12:48.545 --> 00:12:51.050
I just go, "Oh, what a plan.

00:12:51.050 --> 00:12:53.733
Oh, what a planner.

00:12:57.311 --> 00:13:01.480
" And I just go, the only one that could do this is the hand of the Lord.

00:13:01.480 --> 00:13:04.000
This isn't just normal.

00:13:04.000 --> 00:13:08.049
We are living in the last of the last days.

00:13:23.400 --> 00:13:24.010
I encourage you, if you're upset inside today and you're fearful of all the things that I'm seeing, and I live in this area and people are freaked out, the Lord said the Lord will give strength unto his people.

00:13:24.010 --> 00:13:25.839
This is Psalms 29:11.

00:13:25.839 --> 00:13:30.230
The Lord will give strength unto his people.

00:13:46.760 --> 00:13:46.995
The Lord will bless his people with peace.

00:13:46.995 --> 00:14:01.820
I believe with all my heart that we are a people that walks in peace and we're not going to be tormented by fear of what we see on the news.

00:14:01.820 --> 00:14:09.472
I'm not ever trying to scare you; I'm trying to prepare you.

00:14:09.472 --> 00:14:22.950
I'm trying to warn you of what I see coming as a watchman to tell you this is the darkness of the hour.

00:14:22.950 --> 00:14:33.507
It's going to get dark, and it's going to get really light in the church, but it's going to take you knowing who you are.

00:14:33.507 --> 00:14:38.560
If you don't know Psalms 91 and Psalms 23, the Lord said you're in trouble.

00:14:52.465 --> 00:14:52.680
You need to understand, not just read it once.

00:14:52.680 --> 00:15:05.168
I'm talking about being rooted and grounded in the word of God, having that foundation of a rhema word inside of you, knowing who you are in these last days.

00:15:05.168 --> 00:15:09.080
Knowing that no weapon formed against you is going to prosper.

00:15:09.960 --> 00:15:16.646
I don't care if a thousand of those rockets are flying by my head and 10,000 on my right hand.

00:15:16.646 --> 00:15:18.800
Nothing shall come near me.

00:15:18.800 --> 00:15:19.680
Why?

00:15:19.680 --> 00:15:29.560
Because he keeps his angels and gives his angels charge over me to bear me up in their hands lest I dash my foot against a stone.

00:15:42.352 --> 00:15:42.600
I believe every one of us all around the world is about to see things we never thought we would see.

00:15:42.848 --> 00:16:06.030
A lot of people didn't want to see it, but we're seeing it, and a great shaking to awaken even in America, the Lord said, will come in the days ahead, and the church will wake up out of their slumber.

00:16:06.040 --> 00:16:07.240
So, are we afraid?

00:16:07.240 --> 00:16:09.013
No, we're not afraid.

00:16:09.013 --> 00:16:10.578
We have peace.

00:16:12.872 --> 00:16:13.628
The Lord will bless his people with peace.

00:16:19.920 --> 00:16:21.223
I stay in that peace that passes all understanding because my mind is stayed on him because I trust in him.

00:16:32.920 --> 00:16:33.160
Why?

00:16:33.160 --> 00:16:35.380
Because he has my life.

00:16:35.380 --> 00:16:42.100
Well, what happens, Brandon, if something takes you out and you go home early?

00:16:42.100 --> 00:16:50.020
To be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord.

00:17:04.319 --> 00:17:04.739
I still win.

00:17:14.669 --> 00:17:15.000
The moment I take my last breath on this earth, I'm going to be with my maker.

00:17:36.490 --> 00:17:36.745
I'm going to be standing before a holy God and I'm going to say, "Thank you, Father.

00:17:42.640 --> 00:17:44.592
" And just like Kathryn Kuhlman said all the time, "Lord, I don't have to tell him I love him.

