Oh, I loved you, Lord.

00:17:47.418 --> 00:17:48.449
Why do I have to tell him?

00:18:03.840 --> 00:18:04.080
Because I showed him every day by what I did that I loved him.

00:18:04.080 --> 00:18:09.960
" What we do right now is a display of our love.

00:18:11.320 --> 00:18:17.458
I don't have to tell you that I love my father.

00:18:24.100 --> 00:18:24.425
I'm showing you right now.

00:18:27.440 --> 00:18:30.640
I'm telling you that Jesus Christ is coming.

00:18:30.640 --> 00:18:32.804
It's time to get your heart right.

00:18:39.160 --> 00:18:39.467
You need to repent.

00:18:56.360 --> 00:18:56.567
You're running out of time.

00:18:56.567 --> 00:19:19.440
If you're living in compromise, if you're living in sin, if you're sleeping around, if you're drinking, you're partying, you're acting like the world, and there's no difference between you and the church, you need to repent.

